    <item>
      <title>Blue Owl 为何加大对私人信贷的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-16/why-blue-owl-is-expanding-into-private-credit-with-atalaya</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Blue Owl Capital 联席首席执行官兼联合创始人 Marc Lipschultz 表示，他预计收购信贷管理公司 Atalaya Capital Management 将带来“巨大的增长”。在接受“彭博未平仓合约”采访时，Lipschultz 还对信贷市场的现状发表了评论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-16/why-blue-owl-is-expanding-into-private-credit-with-atalaya</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 14:32:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
