      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/signa-unit-administrators-mull-seeking-claims-against-advisers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Signa 一家主要部门的破产管理员正在审查主要顾问是否未能正确履行职责，以期为债权人收回资金。]]></description>
